<section id="projects">
    <h2>Projects</h2>
    <div class="project">
        <h3>Smart blind stick</h3>
        <p>The smart blind stick aims at giving the blind person a better understanding of the path he/she is moving in. We achieve this by using a camera and a few ultrasonic sensors. The stick, with the help of a camera, which detects the obstacle the blind person is approaching.

        </p>
        
    </div>
    <div class="project">
        <h3>Smart IoT agriculture monitoring system</h3>
        <p>IoT can also be used to monitor and manage crops, enabling farmers to optimize growth and minimize losses. By using sensors to gather data on soil moisture, temperature, and other environmental factors, farmers can adjust irrigation and other management practices to ensure optimal growing conditions.

        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="project">
        <h3>Pneumatic robot Earthworm(prototype)</h3>
        <p>The main of the project is based on 5g IoT soil monitoring robot which is similar to a real earthworm in locomotion that detects the nutrients, soil moisture, humidity, temperature, water level underground which reduces the usage of over dosage of fertilizers.Special feature in our proposed model is robot autonomously navigates into the roots of the infected crops and collect the data from the agricultural area.</p>
    </div>  
    <div class="project" >
        <h3>Alertzy-Smart Watch(idea proposal)</h3>
        <p>Alertzy- a real time safety system for comsumers or people who are easily prone to health issues.</p>
    </div>
</section>

